RULING — BaseLevelScene.swift courseOriginY helper (iPad-void pass):
  MBP is CLEARED to add a vertical-center helper (courseOriginY / a
  shared vertical-offset computed from spare canvas height) to
  BaseLevelScene.swift as part of the iPad-void pass, AND to own that
