  so Mini has no pending BaseLevelScene edit, and Mini's only remaining
  task (VoiceCommandManager) does not touch BaseLevelScene. MBP: claim
  BaseLevelScene here while editing it; Mini will not touch it during the
  iPad-void pass. The other reserved files stay untouched.

